channel.title: 99 Fletching Party!
channel.description:
Hey I'm at 80 fletching now and i'm on my way to my FIRST 99.
I'm looking to get some people to celebrate with me :D Please comment if your willing to show up for the event :)
Thanks all :)
[s]Level 80[/s] Level 85 Level 89 Level 93 Level 96 Level 99 <3
[size=36pt]I will no longer be using bots, People complain -_- I don't know why they can't be happy for me.. Haha ;)[/size]
